        "id": "902fb900-742b-4a5b-86a7-c729d9e45bff",
        "title": "Strategy game in the medieval era.",
        "status": "published",
        "content": "It is exactly as I expected and hoped for, especially now with the introduction of Dragos.\nThis gamefi contains nice innovations and with the release of dragons it will bring a new dimension to the game. It is great that you can extract resources from the game and use the right strategy to defeat enemies.\n\nThis game has a great potential, I’ve seen many improvements in the last few weeks, but still several bugs and performance issues that has to be fixed, but it is getting better and better.\nThe biggest problem I encountered was with support, it takes a long time for a problem to be resolved, even when it's a payment problem, you have to wait too long, for something you already paid.\n\nBy the way the community is great!\n\nEnjoy and have fun!",
        "author": "c2b313f9-c843-434c-ab83-39ba94c199d1",
        "date_created": "2022-06-26T16:14:19.353Z",
