        "id": "75870fa7-266d-4158-891d-7c0e21baf72b",
        "title": "XENNA - GOOD GAME TO PLAY",
        "status": "published",
        "content": "In general, I think this game is quite good to play. \nHere are what I like:\n- Good graphics. Gameplay is not bad. \n- I only have to log in with email, so easy to enter the game. \n- Each match takes not much time, so I can play many matches. \n\nWhat I don't like:\n- I don't know how to play at first. I think if the game has short tutorials/descriptions before joining the game or in the match, it will be better for a newbie like me.\n- It's lagged when I play the game on my laptop. Maybe my device is weak. So I think it's perfect if the game can go smooth even on a weak laptop.",
        "author": "b5a81d96-d419-4708-938e-a14b231c5ac0",
